{"tid":2374914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[處死式]27歲女子浴室內疑一氧化碳中毒　涉事熱水爐香港以外地方購買","createTime":"2021-01-21T14:44:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T05:18:06.000Z","uid":105567,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"857282bdfd1d0e2a62cf1ae886016210d42f5e41","tid":2374914,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:44:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-21-2021/69803?fbclid=IwAR3Pr_QsJ7GvPPshOHaAxIVoFChkWsCI9lnq0NGlS5E_va6XXoI_PDrrDzc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-21-2021%2F69803%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Pr_QsJ7GvPPshOHaAxIVoFChkWsCI9lnq0NGlS5E_va6XXoI_PDrrDzc&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=0a919c6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-21-2021/69803?fbclid=IwAR3Pr_QsJ7GvPPshOHaAxIVoFChkWsCI9lnq0NGlS5E_va6XXoI_PDrrDzc</a><br />\n<br />\n衞生署衞生防護中心今日（1月21日）表示，昨日接獲東區尤德夫人那打素醫院通報，一宗懷疑使用氣體熱水爐後一氧化碳中毒個案。 該宗個案涉及一名27歲女子，1月19日在家使用氣體熱水爐洗澡，約半小時後被發現在浴室內不省人事，隨即送往屯門醫院，其後轉送東區尤德夫人那打素醫院接受治療。病人現時情況穩定。根據初步的調查資料，該氣體熱水爐是透過網上從香港以外地方購買，而事發時浴室的抽氣扇已損壞了數天，而洗澡時浴室內的門窗全關上，可能因而令浴室內的一氧化碳水平上升。 衞生防護中心表示，一氧化碳為一種無色、無臭、無味的氣體，它是因不完全燃燒含碳燃料（例如木材、天然氣和汽油）而產生的副產品。    曝露於低濃度一氧化碳的人士可能出現頭暈、頭痛、疲倦和噁心等症狀；而曝露於高濃度一氧化碳的人士則可能出現視覺受損、協調紊亂、失去知覺和腦部受損等症狀，甚至死亡。 衞生防護中心提醒市民，須確保在使用氣體熱水爐時室內有良好的通風。市民如懷疑出現一氧化碳中毒症狀，應立即求醫。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-21-2021/69803?fbclid=IwAR3Pr_QsJ7GvPPshOHaAxIVoFChkWsCI9lnq0NGlS5E_va6XXoI_PDrrDzc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-21-2021%2F69803%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Pr_QsJ7GvPPshOHaAxIVoFChkWsCI9lnq0NGlS5E_va6XXoI_PDrrDzc&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcGHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=0a919c6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-21-2021/69803?fbclid=IwAR3Pr_QsJ7GvPPshOHaAxIVoFChkWsCI9lnq0NGlS5E_va6XXoI_PDrrDzc</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2021"},{"pid":"1af7591e5b0c898f732cdcda0df2090d4b8c4701","tid":2374914,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:48:12.000Z","msg":"淘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863d99050615da49a4b9ebf591a78cc3ae9b2495","tid":2374914,"uid":288648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:49:04.000Z","msg":"如果唔係淘寶咁點？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一陣又炒車"},{"pid":"eb20729b86bd8b6b88d6416c8b4c6e8c90b9d2ac","tid":2374914,"uid":120499,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"親，用淘寶網嗎？<br />\n<br />\n平幾舊，送埋條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e461affd28ca61654baef0a453f33d460acdbb92","tid":2374914,"uid":44454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:49:22.000Z","msg":"淘碳生零"},{"pid":"42253e579d236e5c45ac9c4dc7ae1ce057866c4b","tid":2374914,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:50:38.000Z","msg":"點解會先去屯門再轉去東區嘅醫院<br />\n<br />\n有咩嗰間先做到？"},{"pid":"ce053b10485ebee23e860126107645f4142588d9","tid":2374914,"uid":38904,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6qM74cT.jpg&amp;h=1bcf9445&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"b6650b523c307ae3cc0cef95f7d7e8d4171ccf5f","tid":2374914,"uid":93277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T14:51:42.000Z","msg":"唔爆炸死都毒撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c769cb859380627cd03daefce745247e2156e40","tid":2374914,"uid":33028,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"ce053b10485ebee23e860126107645f414